        "headings": [],
        "body": "In the past, RxCheck required each integrated healthcare entity to have its own SRS server. With the Vendor Connect enhancement, a vendor may utilize a single SRS server to connect multiple healthcare entities to RxCheck. For vendors who wish to utilize a single SRS server for multiple HCE\u2019s, several conditions need to be met. This section outlines those requirements and provides a checklist to assist with implementation of this feature. The following subsection details the requirements for utilizing a single SRS server for multiple HCE\u2019s."
